CreateBudgetChangeOrderCommentForm is an ActionForm
    action is Create
    title is "BudgetChangeRequestComment"
    Layout
        single column
            BudgetChangeOrder
                label is "ChangeRequest"
                display as text
            Subject
            Comment
                use text area of 3 lines
            From
            visible when (HasComment)
                CommentDate
                    display as text
        header5 of "Attachment"
        single column
            Attachment.Title
        paragraph
            Attachment.File
